<b>Dear {!relatedTo.Lead__r.Name},</b>

<p>Congratulations    on taking your first step to reach for the skies, welcome to <b>FSTC!!!</b></p>
<br/>

<p><b>About our Company</b></p>

<p>Founded in 2012, Flight Simulation Technique Centre (FSTC) is the 1st and largest ATO 
(Approved Training Organization) certified by both the Directorate General of Civil Aviation 
(DGCA) and European Union Aviation Safety (EASA) in the country. We are the <b>only
training organization in India that independently own and operate a Flying School (FTO) and </b>an ATO. This gives our students a unique advantage whereby they can complete their entire training with us,
from the single-engine Cessna to the Airbus and Boeing, we train the ‘Complete’ pilot.</p>
<br/>
<p><b>Our Infrastructure</b></p>

<p><b>Offices</b> - Corporate offices and ATO training centers in Gurugram and Hyderabad.</p>


<p>FSTC Flying School - 2 Flying Bases in Bhiwani and Narnaul boast State-of-the-art Infrastructure and brand-new Trainer Aircraft with Glass Cockpits.
Unrestricted Airspace ensures continuous flying at both our bases and their proximity to DEL/NCR region provides a unique convenience factor. 
Quality Flying Instructors and an International Training Curriculum further ensure our students get the best training comparable to anywhere in the world.
We are further expanding and will be opening 4 new flying bases by the year-end.</p>     


<p><b>FSTC ATO</b> - We operate 8 Full Flight Level - D Simulators, the highest by an Indian ATO operator belonging to Boeing, Airbus, 
ATR 72-500/600, and Q400 aircraft.</p>
<p><b>Our Mission and Values</b></p>
<p>India has successfully managed, during the past decade, to ensure a world-leading position in Global Aviation and our aim is to
irrefutably establish India as a Self-Reliant nation in Pilot Training. We pride ourselves in the quality of training we impart, 
our focus has and will always be to make you the best pilot you can be.</p>
<p><b> We hope that your association with us will be productive, meaningful, and long-term and we looking forward 
to helping you achieve your dreams of becoming a pilot.
Our detailed brochure is attached for your reference.</b></p>
<p>The Professional Fee for the <b>FSTC - Flying School &nbsp;<u> {!relatedTo.Select_Course_Name__c}</u> &nbsp;course will be INR &nbsp;<u>{!relatedTo.Total_Price__c}</u> &nbsp; <u>Rs. {!relatedTo.Total_Price_In_Words__c} </u>.</b>&nbsp; Please confirm and acknowledge your participation by this 
week and deposit the initial registration fee for the course into the FSTC Flying School Current account through NEFT/RTGS/Cheque. </p>
<br/>

